          <title>Any tools and tutorials on rails and activitypub?</title>
          <dc:creator><![CDATA[RubyGoddess]]></dc:creator>
          <category>Ruby</category>
          <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I recently discovered <a href="https://pump.io" rel="nofollow noopener">pump.io</a>, activitypub and the concept of “federated” networks. One of my friends invited me to the network mastodon.<br>
I realized mastodon itself is written in ruby. I’m curious, is there anyway to make our rails apps federated? I did a bit of search but I found some of those projects are discontinued. And if yes, is there any tutorials?</p>
